2026-05-15T21:38:42.5810803Z 13    <!--
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5811404Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5812334Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5813587Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5814534Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5815571Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5846789Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5847460Z 20    -->
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5848135Z 21    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT" />
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5849240Z 21-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:5-81
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5850345Z 21-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:22-78
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5851144Z 22    <!--
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5851742Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5852497Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5853499Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5854389Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5855254Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5856334Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5857196Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5858064Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5858892Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5859684Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5860315Z 33    -->
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5860950Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5862038Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:5-79
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5863145Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:22-76
2026-05-15T21:38:42.5864423Z 35    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_EXACT_ALARM" />
