2026-05-15T21:38:42.6294685Z 250        <!--
2026-05-15T21:38:42.6295327Z 251            Same hardening for Glance's InvisibleActionTrampolineActivity.
2026-05-15T21:38:42.6296521Z 252            The library entry is singleInstance with its own taskAffinity
2026-05-15T21:38:42.6297367Z 253            but omits excludeFromRecents (unlike its sibling
2026-05-15T21:38:42.6298202Z 254            ActionTrampolineActivity which already has it). When the
2026-05-15T21:38:42.6299096Z 255            process dies before the trampoline finishes, the system can
2026-05-15T21:38:42.6299990Z 256            restore the task from Recents and replay onCreate with a
2026-05-15T21:38:42.6301134Z 257            stale Intent whose ACTION_INTENT extra is missing — which
2026-05-15T21:38:42.6302015Z 258            triggers an IllegalArgumentException ("List adapter activity
2026-05-15T21:38:42.6302913Z 259            trampoline invoked without specifying target intent"). Adding
2026-05-15T21:38:42.6303819Z 260            excludeFromRecents removes the Recents restoration vector,
2026-05-15T21:38:42.6304754Z 261            matching what Glance already does for ActionTrampolineActivity.
