2026-05-15T21:38:42.9888951Z 56        mediaPlayback foreground service because Samsung One UI suppresses
2026-05-15T21:38:42.9889323Z 57        FOREGROUND_SERVICE_SPECIAL_USE notifications, preventing the
2026-05-15T21:38:42.9889699Z 58        ongoing countdown notification from appearing on those devices.
